title: Agents of S.H.I.E.L.D., Vol. 1: The Coulson Protocols
description: It's high-stakes espionage in the Marvel Universe! Inspired by the hit television series Marvel's Agents of S.H.I.E.L.D. Tony Stark joins Agent Phil Coulson's covert team for a top-secret mission! Collecting Agents of S.H.I.E.L.D. Vol.3 #1-6 and All-New All Different Point One #1.
author: Marc Guggenheim
